frames.caption: In a whimsical scene, chefs are depicted as miniature figures working in a bakery, surrounded by oversized pastries and industrial baking equipment. The setting is illuminated by large overhead lights, casting a warm glow over the bustling activity. The chefs are engaged in various tasks, from kneading dough to arranging baked goods.
frames.description: The scene portrays a fantastical bakery where miniature chefs are busy preparing an array of pastries. The setting is industrial with large ovens and baking equipment, creating an imaginative contrast with the tiny figures and oversized baked goods.

frames.caption: In a bustling bakery, miniature chefs meticulously prepare an array of colorful pastries under the warm glow of industrial lamps. Two women in traditional attire oversee the process, adding a cultural touch to the culinary setting.
